OL,3,CStrikes planned by more than 350
OL,4,CBirmingham bin workers to triple
OL,6,FBin workers in Birmingham are
OL,7,Fdramatically increasing the number of
OL,8,Fplanned strike days in their dispute
OL,9,Fwith the city council over job losses
OL,10,Fand pay cuts.
OL,12,FUnite has announced that strike action
OL,13,Fwill triple from what had been
OL,14,Fpreviously announced from four to 12
OL,15,Fdays in February and from four to 13
OL,16,Fdays in March.
OL,18,FThe dispute was sparked by the
OL,19,Fcouncil's decision to abolish the
OL,20,FWaste Recycling and Collection Officer
OL,21,F(WRCO) role.
