OL,3,CStrikes planned by more than 350
OL,4,CBirmingham bin workers to triple
OL,6,FUnite says this role is 'safety
OL,7,Fcritical' and will result in pay cuts
OL,8,Fof up to #8000 for 150 workers. They
OL,9,Falso fear it is the start of more cuts
OL,10,Fin the service.
OL,12,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,13,Fsaid: 'There is no justification for
OL,14,Fsuch huge pay cuts to workers' wages.
OL,16,F'Birmingham council cannot just ignore
OL,17,Fthis situation and hope that it will
OL,18,Fgo away.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
