OL,3,CStrikes planned by more than 350
OL,4,CBirmingham bin workers to triple
OL,6,F'It is a line in the sand for our
OL,7,Fmembers, who know more attacks will
OL,8,Ffollow if they don't fight back. Unite
OL,9,Fis with them 100 per cent.'
OL,11,FThe escalation means that the next
OL,12,Fstrike day begins tomorrow (4
OL,13,FFebruary) rather than 7 February.
OL,15,FWhen are bin workers striking in
OL,16,FBirmingham this year?
OL,18,F4, 6, 7, 10, 12, 14, 17, 18, 20, 25,
OL,19,F26 and 27
