OL,9,FSince the council effectively declared
OL,10,Fbankruptcy in September 2023, refuse
OL,11,Fworkers have accepted cuts to their
OL,12,Fpay and terms and conditions and
OL,13,Fworked with management in good faith
OL,14,Fto ensure services continued.
OL,16,FThe council then decided to remove the
OL,17,Fsafety critical WRCO role.
