OL,3,CStrikes planned by more than 350
OL,4,CBirmingham bin workers to triple
OL,6,FUnite says the service is heavily
OL,7,Freliant on costly employment agencies
OL,8,Fbecause the council doesn't directly
OL,9,Femploy enough staff.
OL,11,FIt says a number of refuse workers are
OL,12,Femployed through agencies, despite
OL,13,Fhaving performed the role for over a
OL,14,Fdecade.
OL,16,FUnite regional officer Zoe Mayou said:
OL,17,F'Unite's door remains open to
OL,18,Fmeaningful discussions with the
OL,19,Fcouncil to resolving this dispute.
