OL,3,CStrikes planned by more than 350
OL,4,CBirmingham bin workers to triple
OL,6,F'It is the council that bears the
OL,7,Fresponsibility for it escalating. Its
OL,8,Fbehaviour towards its directly
OL,9,Femployed staff is vindictive and does
OL,10,Fnothing to solve the operational
OL,11,Fproblems that are staring it in the
OL,12,Fface."
OL,14,FIn response, a Birmingham City Council
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: 'We are
OL,16,Fdisappointed that this action is
OL,17,Ftaking place, but we are continuing to
OL,18,Fwork through the dispute resolution
OL,19,Fprocedure.
