OL,3,CStrikes planned by more than 350
OL,4,CBirmingham bin workers to triple
OL,6,F'We would like to assure residents
OL,7,Fthat we will do all we can to minimise
OL,8,Fdisruption during any potential
OL,9,Findustrial action.
OL,11,F'We thank residents for their
OL,12,Funderstanding and patience during this
OL,13,Fchallenging period and assure everyone
OL,14,Fthat we are committed to resolving the
OL,15,Fsituation in the best interest of all
OL,16,Fparties involved.
OL,18,F'Up-to-date information will be
OL,19,Fprovided via our website, social media
OL,20,Fand encourage residents to sign up to
OL,21,Fbin collection newsletter.
