OL,4,CBirmingham bin workers to triple
OL,6,F'Ensuring the safety of our employees
OL,7,Fand residents is taken extremely
OL,8,Fseriously, and health and safety is
OL,9,Feveryone's responsibility.
OL,11,F'We have undertaken steps to ensure
OL,12,FBirmingham City Council colleagues
OL,13,Faffected by the change in working
OL,14,Farrangements are supported.
OL,16,F'There are several options that are
OL,17,Favailable to suit different personal
OL,18,Fcircumstances, and of the 170 affected
OL,19,Femployees, over 130 have already opted
OL,20,Ffor redeployment, driver training or
OL,21,Fvoluntary redundancy.
