OL,6,F'We have moved quickly to minimise
OL,7,Fthis period of uncertainty for
OL,8,Feveryone.
OL,10,F'We are committed to working with our
OL,11,Fcolleagues across the service for the
OL,12,Fbest outcome so that we deliver a
OL,13,Fconsistent and reliable service that
OL,14,FBirmingham residents deserve.'
OL,16,FFurther industrial action will be
OL,17,Fscheduled if the dispute is not
OL,18,Fresolved.
